	> Host: 127.0.0.1:3000
	> User-Agent: curl/8.7.1
	> Accept: */*
	>
	* Request completely sent off
	< HTTP/1.1 400 Bad Request
	< Content-Length: 146
	< Content-Type: application/json;charset=UTF-8
	< Date: Sun, 07 Jun 2026 11:42:01 GMT
	< Server: Mojolicious (Perl)
